{
  "text": "In summary, we have proposed a quasi-continuous metasurface to realize the phase modulation of electromagnetic wave. The novel design is characterized by high cross-polarization conversion efficiency within a broadband range covering almost all of the electromagnetic spectrum. This is similar to the ultrabroadband frequency responses (absorption [CITATION_1] 35 and polarization conversion 31 ) given in previous results.",
  "citation_candidates": [
